latestIgtvVideos.title: Qadar Is For Real
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
“Oh Wow! Who’s that girl…”, asked Deepa when she saw Pirtya for the first time. 
Deepa, who plays Cupid in this love story was visiting Canada with her brother when she was smitten with Pirtya’s gorgeous looks and sweet nature. The two became friends and she knew she had to introduce Pirtya to her brother Vijay. 
As the two girls began to set off to their respective homes after the Canada trip, Pirtya extended an invitation to Chile-based Deepa to visit her in New York. Deepa promptly took up the offer, cancelled her flight back to Chile and tagged her unsuspecting brother along to NewYork to visit Pirtya under the guise of ‘some urgent business work’. As the trio met for dinner, Pirtya was introduced to Vijay and the two hit it off instantly. Hours later, he held her hand and led her to the dance floor as Deepa watched all starry eyed at a meant-to-be couple. That’s how it all began. 
All it took was one changed air-ticket as a new flight path dictated a dreamy destiny for two strangers who went from ‘someone’ to ‘someone they couldn’t live without’. For both of them it was ‘LOVE AT FIRST FLIGHT’
